Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,イカロスのような
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:10.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮くな勇気をなくして今　生きてる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:13.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空なりの君を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:20.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それなりにたら　少しでかけらを握りしめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:28.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答えを探すと　明朗になる　
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:34.18,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答えが　ここにあると
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:42.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知れば　すべてが　新しい音色になる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:50.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この風のむこに　確かの輝きが　あるはずさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:58.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その涙はきっと　いつか乾くはずさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:04.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今はまだ　難しくでも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:09.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今は遠く見えても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:13.91,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅かな　微笑みだけない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風を切って
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,息を切らして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:20.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走って来るんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同伊卡洛斯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:10.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们活着 确失去了那份好不容易鼓足的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:13.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望着天空的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:20.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 一定紧握着些许希望的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:28.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追寻答案 带着开朗的心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:34.18,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要的答案 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:42.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这么坚信 这一切将会谱出新的乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:50.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这风的彼端 一定有着最真实的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:58.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那脸庞的泪水 终有一日会风干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:04.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在还有些艰险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:09.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在还有些遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:13.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要一个小小的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们乘风破浪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们屏住呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:20.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑向前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:19.05,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}you are my only shining star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:26.83,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}you are my only shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:28.82,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢動いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.05,0:22:34.24,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人の鼓動触れた時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:41.11,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　今誰を思っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:48.85,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝子星に眺めた切ないその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:55.09,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微かな距離でも届かなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:59.69,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言い訳ばっかりを束ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:02.65,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今を逃げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:06.04,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱虫だったあの頃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:14.04,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れそうな弱さと向き合える気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:17.77,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出すよ 明日の扉開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:21.44,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君が居る場所まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:28.62,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃し続けてきた思い伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:35.91,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here in my house君が笑う 何気ない世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:45.09,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞こえるその声が 私の涙強くする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:48.84,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you are my only shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:19.05,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你是我唯一的启明星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:26.83,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你是划过我生命唯一的流星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:28.82,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想开始悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.05,0:22:34.24,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们触碰到彼此的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:41.11,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正在想念谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:48.85,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过玻璃星星看到你的侧脸 让人如此无法割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:55.09,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使近在咫尺 却也无法向你传达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:59.69,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出种种借口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:02.65,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避着现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:06.04,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我如此胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:14.04,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在终于鼓起勇气直面那溃不成军的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:17.77,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧 打开通向明天的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:21.44,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往你所在的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:28.62,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向你倾诉那份一直未说出口的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:35.91,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这坦诚相对的世界里 向我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:45.09,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你的声音 让我的眼泪也变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:48.84,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是划过我生命唯一的流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好长的银河啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许了什么愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子的话 即使到了东京 也会很出色的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负我 你很高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的话 一定会让和子……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在说什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 向我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君千万……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不认识的男孩子的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在好像快消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn长城特粗圆体\fad(1000,0)}第一话 银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我崭新的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是进藤诹访
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是扬卷和子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她发现你倒在海岸边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要起床吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚是我的肚子……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别笑成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李已经送到宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来爱怎样就怎么样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可乐饼！还有别的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 因为赶不上第一班渡轮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只身跳进海里了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天就迟到是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入学典礼当天乘坐早上第一班的渡轮就足可以赶上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:02:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特纳西·塔科特君 你真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还吃到了这么美味的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 能平安无事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是和子发现你 你就已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特纳西·塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要来这座岛上的学校呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了来做了不起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的事情……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是过上充实的学园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是所谓的「青春的讴歌」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝天 碧海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「要讴歌青春的话 果然还得到南方的海岛啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷说这是所好学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然到这里来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能遇到你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子因为担心你 一大早就来看你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:03:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么特纳西·塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想冒昧地问你一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经经历过初吻了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备作为青春的一大要事去体验
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得人工呼吸包含在接吻之内吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工呼吸……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的救命恩人呢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个可爱的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子小姐可是少爷的未婚妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 人工呼吸是算在接吻的范畴内的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中部也在同一个班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同一个班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你还真是有缘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在诹访君旁边的男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男孩子是不是挺帅的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是特纳西·塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝为何知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事怎么回事怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺熟的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真纪奈琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅长的料理是土豆炖肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想吃土豆炖肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土豆炖肉 不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有生面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟皆水之巫女还挺熟的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 是编入组的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在整理行李吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也住在这栋宿舍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住在岛上 所以没法住进宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这幅画有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我父亲画的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也许就在这岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说那女孩呢 没跟你一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子的话 现在应该在修禊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}修禊（Xì）节是古代春秋两季在水边举行的除去不祥的祭祀活动，农历七月十四日称为“秋禊” 每年七月十四日在水边举行的修禊活动。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修禊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是岛上的巫女之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女之一？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫「四方巫女」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛上有着四位特别的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是你的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事你是从谁那里听到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 在我家族中有着与岛上巫女结婚的惯例
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在如今21世纪 我认为恋爱是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子好像挺中意你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她邀请你一同共进晚餐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来将举行新生的欢迎会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请全体同学务必参加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来宿舍的新生都来齐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是宿舍理事长品田红绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 这可不是笑点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在开餐之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必记住这宿舍的绝对规定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生在三楼 女生在二楼 除此之外都不准进入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除一楼的大厅和食堂之外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室九点之前由女生使用 之后是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有谁违反了这些规定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是违反了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着泳衣做100回单杠翻转上杠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那口红不是违反规定的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是唇膏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得太红了点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是很红的唇膏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲也真是啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要穿着泳衣做100回单杠翻转上杠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 真正会做的也只有红绪罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 哲也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙真的能做到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新来的 听说你是从本岛游过来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太年轻气盛……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能做到这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有潜质啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我们部来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！是拳击部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然打架厉害的会比较受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架跟拳击可不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是二年级的本田逢司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来参观学习一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逢司的花言巧语所迷惑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那张漂亮的脸蛋可是会变得非常惨烈的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别尽说些多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面废弃的矿道很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请千万不要进入围墙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apuribowaze
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的第一阶段将通向一个新的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初始之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,star sword diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 祭典的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力柩和cybody的连接已建立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又向前迈进了一步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是一个大飞跃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位 我们star sword终于解开了气多之巫女的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绮罗星十字团终于来到了第二阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特纳西·塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒着生命危险 渡海而来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真正的目的究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被警告不能去就偏偏要去 这才是男孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充实的学园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就开始享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Pliers（这是把钳子）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 好像有什么东西过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那孩子……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人忘了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Pliers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光从外表看就是群可疑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要对那孩子做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了又能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护弱者是我家的家训
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味逃跑可是什么都保护不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Punch（吃我一拳）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架跟拳击可不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是皆水之巫女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用cybody出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆水的解除应该要到第四阶段才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没接到要把程序提前的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重新定顺序就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我成为第一阶段排第一位的Star Driver的候选人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再拖下去就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供技术帮助的企业股票价格也下跌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说在新藤家留宿的那个少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也来到了金山遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在找他的父亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不抽烟么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓 但是她……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从祭奠撤下的供品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好相处吧 小鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能为我唱首歌么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}飘舞的雪花是星之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}向着天体伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达科塔 达科塔振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}胸口感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}一切都在黑白画面之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你一起来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙想干嘛……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启吧 电力柩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}结上冰霜的白色树干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}冰冷寒气传至双手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}置身于这片森林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}那份温暖变得明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}被悲伤浸染的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apuribowaze
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}是谁的指尖如此温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}在无人知晓的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}等待着黎明的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}我被聚集的光明所洗礼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:17:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}从各处聚集至此的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 Arefisto
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}即使无法再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个封印被解除了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们明白自己在做什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把她放了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}行星如同沙砾一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}安睡之时梦中的残像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&}一切依旧存于黑白记忆之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 从这里往前只有被选中的人才能进入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难以置信 居然创造了这么大的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚禁被启动了的cybody的牢笼竟如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方的封印停止了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 那个是南方的cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南方的巫女守护的这个零时间的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过放了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达科塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你没带面具就能进入这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会在这种地方就被搞定哦 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印记闪光的话会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是银河美少年吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事情和必须要做的事情合二为一的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能听见世界的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起歌颂青春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apuribowaze
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本尊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十二台cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}达科塔所操纵的机器人被称为道伯恩（ダウバーン），其存在被视为一个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道伯恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然坐上了cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三阶段么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊 行动很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道伯恩的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真让人热血沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就是坐上了cybody 少得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你其实还没坐上吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击碎伪装的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已回到了正常的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传送所经历的时间为零
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你因使用Star Driver不力 而被除名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新学期 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.32,0:24:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充实的学园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那些盯上和子的到底是些什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 STAR DRIVER 闪亮的塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.19,0:24:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的银河 一定闪着耀眼光芒！
